00:17:48.100 --> 00:17:50.580
blocking out the very folks who could help him.

00:17:50.580 --> 00:17:55.080
In everyday life, Ian feels better, sharper, more confident

00:17:55.080 --> 00:17:56.680
more effective.

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.320
But it's an illusion.

00:17:58.320 --> 00:18:03.540
With the group's courses pitched at kindergarten levels,
