00:18:25.700 --> 00:18:28.040
These counselling sessions are expensive.

00:18:28.040 --> 00:18:32.360
Sometimes very tiring. But he
frequently emerges feeling lighter.

00:18:32.360 --> 00:18:35.240
The sessions take him further and further into the past

00:18:35.240 --> 00:18:38.460
until he's not quite sure if he's
dealing with real memories.

00:18:38.460 --> 00:18:41.740
Ian visits his parents. He talks about the group.

00:18:41.740 --> 00:18:44.540
His father is concerned about
the money Ian's getting through

00:18:44.540 --> 00:18:46.860
and does an internet search on the group.

00:18:46.860 --> 00:18:48.780
