00:19:04.780 --> 00:19:08.500
Ian agrees to only discuss
superficial subjects with his parents.

00:19:08.500 --> 00:19:12.700
He takes the issue to counselling
to nullify his emotional reaction.

00:19:12.700 --> 00:19:17.520
The groups' noble aim of total freedom for
everyone on the planet has been repackaged.

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:20.820
'Total freedom' now means:
'freedom to do what the group allows'.

00:19:20.820 --> 00:19:25.720
'Everyone on the planet' now means 'everyone who remains uncritical of the group'.

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:28.380
Three years and thousands of dollars later

00:19:28.380 --> 00:19:31.220
Ian's completed two levels of counseling.

00:19:31.220 --> 00:19:35.560
He's also expecting his second child
with his new wife, also a member of the group.

00:19:35.560 --> 00:19:37.360
Time for level three.

00:19:37.360 --> 00:19:42.080
He's led into a room and shown a document
that tells him the following information:

00:19:42.080 --> 00:19:48.760
Millions of years ago, an evil galactic ruler
transported billions of aliens to earth in spaceplanes

00:19:48.760 --> 00:19:50.460
placed them around volcanoes

00:19:50.460 --> 00:19:52.720
and blew them up with nuclear weapons.

00:19:52.720 --> 00:19:57.580
As they departed from their bodies,
